p without art. I bet you all want in your group a SK so he can pull / tank . A cleric so he can heal / rez . a shm / ench for slowing &amp; haste. an ench, bst, dru , nec , brd for mana purposes (might forget some this aint my cup of tea mana ). an ench / brd / nec for mez other classes are welcome but not necessary. this is a zergling group where other classes have no reason to be there , or just to fill the holes.  <br /> <br /> <br />finally this is what i think of mnks:  <br />we are the lasiest players of the game ! We are always sleeping ! <br />why that ? <br />1. We FD on pulls <br />2. we FD when we come into the camp after the pulls  <br />3. we FD while the group is getting wiped <br />4. we even FD on CR while the rogue is frantically sneak / hiding  / running through the zone..  <br />5. finally we sometime stay FD while the group is getting buffed after rezzes and telling the raid / group well uhm .. named XX is still camping me dunno why, and we have full repop here, GL !!  8) .   <br /> <br />I prefer you dislike mnks for those reasons than disliking mnks because you met bad players =) .  <br /> <br /> <br />Cherubin Vindictson , 65 nunn Sister NOT willing to change title ;p <br />Karana server <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Thu May 20 15:08:39 2004 by Gaellian</span></i> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Thu May 20 15:13:07 2004 by Gaellian</span></i></p>
