<p>Monk's don't tank, except for the really stupid ones. But a Monk can come in handy to take the brunt of the attacks. Given a combination of natural Dodge skills, high AC, and HP, with the right armor and buffs, Monks can do very good at distracting while everybody else flees. I apologize to any who I insult in saying this, but thinking that your group can do fine in high level monster zone, without a Monk, is suicidal <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Tue Aug  3 23:17:07 2004 by TiberraTheWolf</span></i></p>
