<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>i guess you have some reason in saying that monks cant tank, but in some cases you are very wrong. for example, what about time geared/ gates geared monks? i know many monks on my server with 6-7kish hp unbuffed. that is better than many tanks, depending on the zone.  also monks have increased damage avoidance and with the proper AAs can be nearly indestructible, again depending on the zone. <br />another issue with tanking obviously is aggro. however, with the right gear and AAs monks can get aggro very easily. just have all the proc AAs and attacking AAs and they can be hitting extremely fast and with many hits, plus high damage procs stealing aggro, and intimidation works well because since most high level mobs resist fear, they can steal it that way. <br />and besides, you only have 4k so your not the greatest tank either :)</p>
